ELIXPO LICENSE
==============

This repository is part of the Elixpo ecosystem and is licensed under the
Elixpo licensing standard. The same standard applies to every repository in
the ecosystem. Any product-specific terms for this repository are declared in
the NOTICE file at the repository root (the "notice board"), which must be read
together with this LICENSE.

The structure of the LICENSES/ directory mirrors the Linux kernel's LICENSES/
tree: canonical license texts live under LICENSES/, this file is the pointer.

